h the use of the recognition</li><li><strong>every 5 years, follow a refresher training</strong> at a <a href=\"https://datasets.omgeving.vlaanderen.be/be.vl.omgeving.erkenningen.distribution.opleidingscentra_technici_stookolietanks.pdf\">recognised training centre</a>. The latest date for following a refresher training can be found at:<ul><li>on your certificate of competence</li><li>or in <a href=\"https://datasets.omgeving.vlaanderen.be/be.vl.omgeving.erkenningen.distribution.technici_stookolietanks.pdf\">the overview lists of recognised fuel oil tank technicians</a>.</li></ul></li><li><strong>report every change of identification data</strong> (such as address, e-mail address) immediately via <a href=\"mailto:erkenningen.omgeving@vlaanderen.be\">erkenningen.omgeving@vlaanderen.be</a></li><li>pay the <a href=\"https://www.dev-vlaanderen.be/vlarel-retributies\">annual fee </a> for the supervision of the recognition. The first payment is to be made in the year following the year in which you obtained the Flemish recognition certificate. Failure to pay the annual fee will lead to automatic suspension of the recognition following a formal notice of default. If the fee is still not paid within 30 days of the suspension, the recognition will automatically lapse.</li></ul><p><a href=\"https://www.dev-vlaanderen.be/informatie-voor-de-technicus-stookolietanks\">More info on the obligations for recognised technicians</a> can be found on the Department of Environment and Spatial Development website.</p>","en-x-generated":"<p>To be approved as a fuel oil tank technician, you must comply with:</p><ul><li><a href=\"https://navigator.emis.vito.be/mijn-navigator?woId=36058\">general recognition conditions</a> that apply to all environmental recognitions<ul><li>in the 3 years preceding the application for the Flemish certificate of recognition, the applicant has not received a criminal conviction in a <a href=\"https://www.dev-vlaanderen.be/uw-overheid/verdeling-van-de-bevoegdheden/de-europese-unie-eu-de-europese-economische-ruimte-eer-het-schengengebied-en-de-eurozone\">member state of the European Economic Area</a> for breaches of environmental legislation relating to the use of the recognition</li><li>in the 2 years preceding the application for the Flemish recognition certificate, no recognition with the same object has been withdrawn from the applicant, for violation of the related obligations of that recognition.</li></ul></li><li><strong>special conditions of recognition</strong>:<ul><li>be a <strong>natural person</strong> </li><li>be in possession of a<strong> certificate of competence for the inspection and maintenance of fuel oil tanks</strong>, issued by a recognised training centre.</li></ul></li></ul><p>More information can be found in <a href=\"https://navigator.emis.vito.be/mijn-navigator?woId=36058\">art. 8 VLAREL (general conditions for recognition)</a> and <a href=\"https://navigator.emis.vito.be/mijn-navigator?woId=36093&amp;woLang=nl\">art. 17 VLAREL (special conditions for recognition)</a>. </p><h3>Period of validity and obligations</h3><p>Recognition is valid for <strong>an indefinite</strong> period. As a recognised technician, you must fulfil some <strong>obligations </strong>to remain recognised. </p><p><a href=\"https://www.dev-vlaanderen.be/informatie-voor-de-technicus-stookolietanks\">More info on the obligations for approved fuel oil tank technicians</a>.</p>","nl-BE-x-formal":"<p>Om erkend te worden als technicus stookolietanks, moet u voldoen aan:</p><ul><li><a href=\"https://navigator.emis.vito.be/mijn-navigator?woId=36058\">algemene erkenningsvoorwaarden</a> die gelden voor alle erkenningen leefmilieu<ul><li>in de 3 jaar die de aanvraag van het Vlaamse erkenningsbewijs voorafgaan, heeft de aanvrager geen strafrechtelijke veroordeling opgelopen in een <a href=\"https://www.dev-vlaanderen.be/uw-overheid/verdeling-van-de-bevoegdheden/de-europese-unie-eu-de-europese-economische-ruimte-eer-het-schengengebied-en-