II, III or IV</strong> <strong>European certificate </strong>. The training centre also registers your certificate in the Flemish government's Learning and Experience Evidence Database (LED).</p><p>The first examination for obtaining the European certificate as a refrigeration technician consists of 4 parts:</p><ul><li>a theoretical part on refrigeration technology</li><li>a theoretical part on legislation</li><li>a practical test handling ozone-depleting substances or fluorinated greenhouse gases</li><li>a brazing test</li></ul><p>Persons wishing to obtain a category III or IV certificate are exempted from the brazing test. The refrigeration technician passes if he obtains at least 60% of the marks for each section. </p><p>Possible examination questions</p><ul><li><a href=\"https://assets.vlaanderen.be/image/upload/v1654077126/20150213_examenvragen_koeltechniek_eerste_examen_jyxy4m.pdf\">First examination in refrigeration technology: list of theoretical questions</a></li><li>Practical test operations with ozone-depleting substances or fluorinated greenhouse gases:<ul><li><a href=\"https://assets.vlaanderen.be/image/upload/v1654077131/20150213_proef_handelingen_koelmiddel_cat_I_vruccm.pdf\">Practical test operation cat. I</a></li><li><a href=\"https://assets.vlaanderen.be/image/upload/v1654077132/20150213_proef_handelingen_koelmiddel_cat_II_mcib7j.pdf\">Field test handling cat. II</a></li><li><a href=\"https://assets.vlaanderen.be/image/upload/v1654077133/20150213_proef_handelingen_koelmiddel_cat_III_xmnuta.pdf\">Field test act cat. III</a></li><li><a href=\"https://assets.vlaanderen.be/image/upload/v1654077134/20150213_proef_handelingen_koelmiddel_cat_IV_kwqcyu.pdf\">Practice test act cat. IV</a></li></ul></li><li>Brazing practical test<ul><li><a href=\"https://assets.vlaanderen.be/image/upload/v1654077127/20150213_hardsoldeerproef_cat_I_rzk1yo.pdf\">Practice test brazing category I</a><ul><li><a href=\"https://assets.vlaanderen.be/image/upload/v1654077135/schema_h